    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="about-main-container contact-main-container">

            
            
            
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="../images/background-image-main.jpg" alt="">
                <h1>Any Query? <br/> Contact Flavor Fusion</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="about-us-content">
                <h3>Have a question or suggestions? </h3>
                <p>We’d love to hear from you! Please fill out the form below with you name, email and query and our team will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
                <p>By reaching out, you’re not just contacting us; you’re becoming part of us.</p>
                <p>
                    We are excited to connect and assist you on your culinary journey!
                    </p>
            </div>
            
            
